                          PortageII_cur source code

Contents of this directory:

   Makefile         top-level Makefile for building PortageII_cur
   Makefile.user-conf  user-configurable build parameters

   adaptation/      mixture-model adaptation (training of mixture LMs and TMs)
   build/           tools for compiling and installing
   canoe/           decoder, including code for using translation models
   confidence/      confidence estimation
   distortion/      lexicalized distortion model training
   eval/            code for automatic evaluation of MT output
   htmldoc/         generated code documentation (start at htmldoc/index.html)
   lm/              library for using various types of language models
   logging/         logging facility for debugging
   preprocessing/   markup, tokenization, and other linguistically-motivated
                    text processing
   rescoring/       nbest list reordering using a variety of features
   textutils/       basic text processing utilities
   tm/              code for creating translation models
   tp_models/       tightly packed models: TPPTs, TPLMs
   tpt/             tightly packed tries, suffix arrays and related code
   truecasing/      restore natural case to text
   utils/           basic tools for other modules to use
   word_align/      word-alignment related code
